<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạảbānā ạản̊ta ạl̊maṣ̊daru
 lil̊kẖaẙri wāllũṭ̊fi ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 fī ạb̊nika qad̊ bārak̊tanā
 bikulĩ jūdiⁿ yā karīm̊

[V2]
 2- fāi̹nãka ạảḥ̊bab̊tanā
 ḥatãy̱ manaḥ̊tanā ạl̊ḥayāh̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ māta ʿanãạ fid̊yaẗaⁿ
 rabũ ạl̊ḥayāẗi wālnãjāh̊

[V3]
 3- bal̊ fīhi qadi ạkẖ̊tar̊tanā
 qab̊la ạlzãmāni ạlạảzalī̃̊
 biniʿ̊maẗiⁿ ʿajībaẗiⁿ
 fālsẖũk̊ru lạis̊mika ạl̊ʿalī̃̊

[V4]
 4- wafīhi bika naf̊takẖir̊
 ại̹dẖ̊ bihi qad̊ ṣālaḥ̊tanā
 wamaʿ̊hu ạảẙḍaⁿạ nan̊taẓir̊
 bitẖiqaẗiⁿ mīrātẖanā

[V5]
 5- wakulũ dẖā ṣāra lanā
 biḥas̊bi qaṣ̊di niʿ̊matik̊
 fālsẖũk̊ra nah̊dīka bihi
 ʿalay̱ jazīli raḥ̊matik̊</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉bạnạ ạ̉nt ạlmṣdr</title>
</song>